-- Monti Says He is Willing to ‘Guide’ Parties That Back his Agenda
-- B y   A n d r e w   D a v i s
-- 2012-12-23T11:47:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-12-23/monti-says-he-is-willing-to-guide-parties-that-back-his-agenda.html
Italian Prime Miniser  Mario Monti 
said he is willing to suppport any parties adopting his platform
for Italy and would be willing to “guide” those forces if they
win the elections.
*Monti won’t lead any specific party in February elections
*Monti says he is in the hands of the parties that adhere to his
